All wins on the first 3 reels trigger the Multiplier Feature on the separate Multiplier Reels.
All pays are multiplied by the multiplier appearing on the middle position of the first Multiplier Reel. If another multiplier appears on the middle position of the second Multiplier reel, it is multiplied again by that multiplier.
The Worm hole symbol ends the Multiplier Feature.
Wild symbol substitutes for all symbols except Multiplier symbols!

The game pays 27 ways.
Bet ways win when matching symbols appear anywhere on adjacent reels from leftmost to right
WINS ON EACH BET WAY ARE MULTIPLIED BY THE BET LEVEL Betway wins pay if in succession from leftmost to right. Malfunction voids all pays.
Multiply your win up to 100 times!
You have an unfinished game. Click OK to see result of pending bet.
